      <title>消息称花旗并购资深人士 Cary Kochman 将退休</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/citi-ma-veteran-cary-kochman-retire-sources-say-2024-12-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士周四向路透社透露，花旗集团顶级交易员之一卡里·科赫曼 (Cary Kochman) 即将退休，此前他已执掌这家华尔街银行的并购集团近 14 年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/citi-ma-veteran-cary-kochman-retire-sources-say-2024-12-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 16:13:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沃达丰与Three合并案获批标志着英国反垄断政策转变</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/vodafone-three-merger-approval-marks-uk-antitrust-shift-2024-12-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国决定允许四大移动网络中的两家进行合并，这是监管机构接受政府意愿的第一个重要迹象，政府希望监管机构优先考虑经济增长和基础设施投资，而不是降低消费者价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/vodafone-three-merger-approval-marks-uk-antitrust-shift-2024-12-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 15:18:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰首席执行官继续改组，更多高级管理人员将离职</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-announces-senior-management-exits-global-reorganisation-continues-2024-12-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰银行周四宣布了一系列高级管理人员的离职和任命，首席执行官乔治斯·埃尔赫德里 (Georges Elhedery) 完成了旨在精简成本和改善决策的全面改革的第一阶段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-announces-senior-management-exits-global-reorganisation-continues-2024-12-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 13:12:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙 CNMV 将等待反垄断审查以决定 BBVA-Sabadell 交易</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/spains-cnmv-will-wait-antitrust-review-decide-bbva-sabadell-deal-2024-12-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙证券市场监管机构 CNMV 负责人罗德里戈·布埃纳文图拉 (Rodrigo Buenaventura) 周四对记者表示，CNMV 将等待竞争监管机构对 BBVA 恶意收购萨瓦德尔的审查结果，然后才决定是否批准收购招股说明书。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/spains-cnmv-will-wait-antitrust-review-decide-bbva-sabadell-deal-2024-12-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 12:39:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
